      "financial_assets": [
        "ETH held by TraitForgeNft during mint flows (transient; forwarded to NukeFund via _distributeFunds)",
        "ETH held by NukeFund as internal-accounted 'fund' (claim pool for nuke payouts)",
        "ETH held by NukeFund contract balance that is not reflected in 'fund' (e.g., forced ETH via selfdestruct, direct sends bypassing receive?; accounting mismatch risk)",
